最新版本:  4.24.2

Thanks for using Calm! This update contains multiple bug fixes and performance improvements.

Be sure to listen to our newest Sleep Stories including “The Golden Arrow,” narrated by Calm Community favorite Erik Braa, where you’ll take a trip on trains and ferries all the way from London to Paris. Or journey through a selection of Calm Classics with one of our beloved narrators in the “Best of Alan Sklar - Anthology.” And don’t forget to listen to world-renowned actor Matthew McConaughey’s dreamy story about the mysteries of the universe in “Wonder.”

Relax deeply and fall asleep peacefully with six new music tracks from Liquid Mind by composer Chuck Wild.

Check out our popular meditation program by Jeff Warren, known for his dynamic and accessible style of teaching, titled “How to Meditate.” It’s a simple 30-day program for everyone.

As always, you can expect an original Daily Calm every day, new Sleep Stories every week, and new meditation programs.

While you’re waiting for the update to install, try this simple practice: Relax your body and get comfortable, then turn your attention to the breath. Keeping the rhythm of your breathing natural, just observe your breath as it flows in and out. Notice how it moves in and out of the body with curiosity. Breathe each breath as though for the very first time.
